videos.headline: Stewart cans early 3
videos.description: Breanna Stewart pops open behind the 3-point line and knocks down the jumper.

videos.headline: Hamby's heads up play at the buzzer gives Aces the lead
videos.description: Dearica Hamby picks off the inbounds pass and lays it in giving the Aces the one point lead heading into the second quarter.

tracking.trackingName: WNBA_One-Play (Hamby’s heads up play at the buzzer gives Aces the lead) 2020/08/22 ESHEET

videos.headline: Wilson knocks down the stepback jumper
videos.description: A'ja Wilson shows off her outside game as she steps back and nails the jumper.

tracking.trackingName: WNBA_One-Play (Wilson knocks down the stepback jumper) 2020/08/22 ESHEET

videos.headline: Bird takes shot at Fever
videos.description: After the Fever were disappointed that Sue Bird didn't play against them, Bird said she doesn't make a decision on whether to play based on opponents, especially Indiana.

tracking.trackingName: COM_WNBA Interview (Bird takes shot at Fever) 2020/08/22 ESHEET

videos.headline: Aces' steal leads to Wilson's layup
videos.description: The Aces get the steal and finish with an A'ja Wilson layup giving them their first 20-point lead of the game.

tracking.trackingName: WNBA_One-Play (Aces’ steal leads to Wilson’s layup) 2020/08/22 ESHEET

videos.headline: Wilson denies Stewart at the rim
videos.description: Breanna Stewart tries to get the layup past A'ja Wilson, but she is denied as the ball is swatted out of bounds.

tracking.trackingName: WNBA_One-Play (Wilson denies Stewart at the rim) 2020/08/22 ESHEET
